Invocation Name: the domesticated duck
des:
Listen to this interactive story with a timeless lesson. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. 
Weather is unpredictable in the South Dakota Plains, but the ways of my ancestors are clear to me, they flew away, far from the world of dark clouds to a world beyond the sky, where the true Sun, our star shines bright and the weather is always pleasant. 
Discover the story of Mac. a domesticated duck who could not think beyond Father Bulb, discover his true parents, the way to the constellations, the ways of the wind and joins his wild duck cousins, beyond the blue sky?
The blue sky is an open invitation to flight, one with our true self, but will the sky be high?
